*glitz-0.3.0.20050115 (23 Feb 2005)

  23 Feb 2005; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  +glitz-0.3.0.20050115.ebuild:
  Add a version of 0.3.0 taken from a CVS snapshot. Works with the latest
  cairo-0.3.0 release (unlike glitz-0.4.0). See bug #79640. Add myself as a
  maintainer.

  06 Feb 2005; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> glitz-0.2.3.ebuild:
  Added ~ppc64 to KEYWORDS

  26 Jan 2005; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> glitz-0.4.0.ebuild:
  Added ~ppc64 to KEYWORDS

